data.description: Welcome to this beautiful Downtown Covington Modern Farmhouse retreat within the golf cart district. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances including the 48-inch double oven chef gas range with pot filler, quartz countertops, a farm sink, and an island that opens to the cozy living room with a gas fireplace, perfect for entertaining or creating new memories.    The Owner's Spa En Suite on the Main Level and the added electric charging port for your electric car, are a bonus to this must-see home!  This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath historic picturesque home with original hardwood floors over 100 years old, offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm offering a peaceful retreat while being conveniently located just minutes away from Covington's charming square area, with its unique shops, delicious dining options, and vibrant community events.  Whether you enjoy swinging on the front porch swing, sitting on the screened side porch, planting in the yard, or entertaining while cooking your favorite meal, this no-HOA home is near schools, amenities, Three Ring film studio, and major highways, ensuring convenience without sacrificing the tranquility of rural living.   Schedule your showing today and experience the allure of this captivating farmhouse firsthand.   Your peaceful oasis awaits!   The home is virtually staged
